			<div class="container px-5 my-5">
				<div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
					<div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-7">
						<div class="text-center">
							<h2 class="fw-bolder text-white">Новые релизы</h2>
							<p class="lead fw-normal text-white-50 mb-5">Будьте в курсе последних глав!</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row gx-5">
					<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
						<div class="card h-100 shadow border-0" style="background-color: #3a3a52;">
							<img  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='./images/where.gif'" class="card-img-top" src="https://example.com/manga1.jpg" alt="Manga 1" />
							<div class="card-body p-4">
								<div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2" style="background-color: #6a5acd;">Новинка</div>
								<a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="#!"><h5 class="card-title mb-3 text-white">Токийский гуль: Реинкарнация</h5></a>
								<p class="card-text mb-0 text-white-50">Продолжение истории о людях, ставших гулями.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="card-footer p-4 pt-0 bg-transparent border-top-0">
								<div class="d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
									<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
										<img  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='./images/where.gif'" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="40px" height="40px" src="https://example.com/author1.jpg" alt="Author 1" />
										<div class="small">
											<div class="fw-bold text-white">Сотрудник 1</div>
											<div class="text-muted">October 1, 2023 &middot; 5 min read</div>
