							<img  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='./images/where.gif'" class="card-img-top" src="https://example.com/manga2.jpg" alt="Manga 2" />
							<div class="card-body p-4">
								<div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2" style="background-color: #6a5acd;">Новинка</div>
								<a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="#!"><h5 class="card-title mb-3 text-white">Моя геройская академия: Восстание</h5></a>
								<p class="card-text mb-0 text-white-50">Продолжение истории о героях и злодеях.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="card-footer p-4 pt-0 bg-transparent border-top-0">
								<div class="d-flex align-items-end justify-content-between">
									<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
										<img  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='./images/where.gif'" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="40px" height="40px" src="https://example.com/author2.jpg" alt="Author 2" />
										<div class="small">
											<div class="fw-bold text-white">Сотрудник 2</div>
											<div class="text-muted">September 25, 2023 &middot; 4 min read</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
						<div class="card h-100 shadow border-0" style="background-color: #3a3a52;">
							<img  onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='./images/where.gif'" class="card-img-top" src="https://example.com/manga3.jpg" alt="Manga 3" />
							<div class="card-body p-4">
								<div class="badge bg-primary bg-gradient rounded-pill mb-2" style="background-color: #6a5acd;">Новинка</div>
								<a class="text-decoration-none link-dark stretched-link" href="#!"><h5 class="card-title mb-3 text-white">Атака титанов: Последний выстрел</h5></a>
